original_text: Neither did Naphtali drive out the inhabitants of Bethshemesh, nor the inhabitants of Bethanath; but he dwelt among the Canaanites, the inhabitants of the land: nevertheless the inhabitants of Bethshemesh and of Bethanath became tributaries unto them.
korean_text: 납달리는 벧세메스 주민과 벧아낫 주민을 쫓아내지 못하고 그 땅의 주민 가나안 족속 가운데 거주하였으나 벧세메스와 벧아낫 주민들이 그들에게 노역을 하였더라

sentences.original_text: Neither did Naphtali drive out the inhabitants of Bethshemesh
but he dwelt among the Canaanites
sentences.korean_translation: 그러나 그는 가나안 사람들 중에 거주했고

sentences.original_text: and of Bethanath became tributaries unto them
sentences.korean_translation: 벧아닷 주민들은 그들에게 조공을 바치는 자가 되었다
